USE:
-------------------------------------------------------
--Build distribucion.cpp--

g++ -Wall -o Distribucion "%e" "%f" -std=c++11
-------------------------------------------------------
--Generate distribution files--

./distribucion	n	train.txt	generated.txt

(n= n-grames length, 
we recommend 4 for chi and jaccard and 10 for jacccard)
-------------------------------------------------------
--Run chi.py, jaccard.py or totalvariation.py--

./chi.py
./jaccard.py
./totalvariation.py
-------------------------------------------------------

///////////////////////////////////////////////////////
./testvariation.cpp	p       old.txt	   modified.txt

Goes throw every char in old.txt, each char has 1/p 
chance of being modified (for a another random char)
///////////////////////////////////////////////////////
